{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":875,"text":"I'm a lifelong traveler."},{"time":2783,"text":"Even as a little kid,"},{"time":4442,"text":"I was actually working out\nthat it would be cheaper"},{"time":7922,"text":"to go to boarding school in England"},{"time":10048,"text":"than just to the best school down the road\nfrom my parents' house in California."},{"time":15168,"text":"So, from the time I was nine years old"},{"time":18547,"text":"I was flying alone several times a year"},{"time":21775,"text":"over the North Pole, just to go to school."},{"time":25241,"text":"And of course the more I flew\nthe more I came to love to fly,"},{"time":28884,"text":"so the very week after I graduated\nfrom high school,"},{"time":32150,"text":"I got a job mopping tables"},{"time":34864,"text":"so that I could spend\nevery season of my 18th year"},{"time":39065,"text":"on a different continent."},{"time":42066,"text":"And then, almost inevitably,\nI became a travel writer"},{"time":46187,"text":"so my job and my joy could become one."},{"time":50636,"text":"And I really began to feel\nthat if you were lucky enough"},{"time":54522,"text":"to walk around\nthe candlelit temples of Tibet"},{"time":57954,"text":"or to wander along the seafronts in Havana"},{"time":60758,"text":"with music passing all around you,"},{"time":63138,"text":"you could bring those sounds \nand the high cobalt skies"},{"time":66435,"text":"and the flash of the blue ocean"},{"time":68777,"text":"back to your friends at home,"},{"time":70790,"text":"and really bring some magic"},{"time":72581,"text":"and clarity to your own life."},{"time":75402,"text":"Except, as you all know,"},{"time":77868,"text":"one of the first things you learn\nwhen you travel"},{"time":80700,"text":"is that nowhere is magical\nunless you can bring the right eyes to it."},{"time":86078,"text":"You take an angry man to the Himalayas,"},{"time":88557,"text":"he just starts complaining about the food."},{"time":91873,"text":"And I found that the best way"},{"time":94395,"text":"that I could develop more attentive\nand more appreciative eyes"},{"time":98439,"text":"was, oddly,"},{"time":100037,"text":"by going nowhere, just by sitting still."},{"time":103505,"text":"And of course sitting still\nis how many of us get"},{"time":106354,"text":"what we most crave and need\nin our accelerated lives, a break."},{"time":112124,"text":"But it was also the only way"},{"time":113846,"text":"that I could find to sift through\nthe slideshow of my experience"},{"time":119347,"text":"and make sense of the future and the past."},{"time":122631,"text":"And so, to my great surprise,"},{"time":125673,"text":"I found that going nowhere"},{"time":127579,"text":"was at least as exciting\nas going to Tibet or to Cuba."},{"time":131697,"text":"And by going nowhere,\nI mean nothing more intimidating"},{"time":135752,"text":"than taking a few minutes out of every day"},{"time":138584,"text":"or a few days out of every season,"},{"time":140555,"text":"or even, as some people do,"},{"time":142524,"text":"a few years out of a life"},{"time":145343,"text":"in order to sit still long enough"},{"time":148044,"text":"to find out what moves you most,"},{"time":151435,"text":"to recall where your truest happiness lies"},{"time":154779,"text":"and to remember that sometimes"},{"time":156549,"text":"making a living and making a life"},{"time":159264,"text":"point in opposite directions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":162457,"text":"And of course, this is what wise beings\nthrough the centuries"},{"time":165654,"text":"from every tradition have been telling us."},{"time":167897,"text":"It's an old idea."},{"time":169823,"text":"More than 2,000 years ago, \nthe Stoics were reminding us"},{"time":173117,"text":"it's not our experience\nthat makes our lives,"},{"time":176171,"text":"it's what we do with it."},{"time":178379,"text":"Imagine a hurricane suddenly \nsweeps through your town"},{"time":182231,"text":"and reduces every last thing to rubble."},{"time":186739,"text":"One man is traumatized for life."},{"time":190401,"text":"But another, maybe even his brother,\nalmost feels liberated,"},{"time":194265,"text":"and decides this is a great chance\nto start his life anew."},{"time":198507,"text":"It's exactly the same event,"},{"time":200357,"text":"but radically different responses."},{"time":202909,"text":"There is nothing either good or bad,\nas Shakespeare told us in \"Hamlet,\""},{"time":207300,"text":"but thinking makes it so."},{"time":210720,"text":"And this has certainly been\nmy experience as a traveler."},{"time":214060,"text":"Twenty-four years ago I took \nthe most mind-bending trip"},{"time":217233,"text":"across North Korea."},{"time":219915,"text":"But the trip lasted a few days."},{"time":222804,"text":"What I've done with it sitting still,\ngoing back to it in my head,"},{"time":226384,"text":"trying to understand it,\nfinding a place for it in my thinking,"},{"time":230056,"text":"that's lasted 24 years already"},{"time":232320,"text":"and will probably last a lifetime."},{"time":235683,"text":"The trip, in other words,\ngave me some amazing sights,"},{"time":239059,"text":"but it's only sitting still"},{"time":241124,"text":"that allows me to turn those\ninto lasting insights."},{"time":244816,"text":"And I sometimes think\nthat so much of our life"},{"time":247762,"text":"takes place inside our heads,"},{"time":249779,"text":"in memory or imagination\nor interpretation or speculation,"},{"time":254592,"text":"that if I really want to change my life"},{"time":257395,"text":"I might best begin by changing my mind."},{"time":261430,"text":"Again, none of this is new;"},{"time":262950,"text":"that's why Shakespeare and the Stoics\nwere telling us this centuries ago,"},{"time":267250,"text":"but Shakespeare never had to face\n200 emails in a day."},{"time":271503,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":272905,"text":"The Stoics, as far as I know,\nwere not on Facebook."},{"time":277228,"text":"We all know that in our on-demand lives,"},{"time":280084,"text":"one of the things that's most on demand"},{"time":282192,"text":"is ourselves."},{"time":283420,"text":"Wherever we are, any time of night or day,"},{"time":286052,"text":"our bosses, junk-mailers,\nour parents can get to us."},{"time":290443,"text":"Sociologists have actually found\nthat in recent years"},{"time":293772,"text":"Americans are working fewer hours\nthan 50 years ago,"},{"time":297230,"text":"but we feel as if we're working more."},{"time":300396,"text":"We have more and more time-saving devices,"},{"time":302942,"text":"but sometimes, it seems,\nless and less time."},{"time":306742,"text":"We can more and more easily \nmake contact with people"},{"time":309226,"text":"on the furthest corners of the planet,"},{"time":311585,"text":"but sometimes in that process"},{"time":313579,"text":"we lose contact with ourselves."},{"time":317325,"text":"And one of my biggest surprises \nas a traveler"},{"time":321118,"text":"has been to find\nthat often it's exactly the people"},{"time":324296,"text":"who have most enabled us to get anywhere"},{"time":327413,"text":"who are intent on going nowhere."},{"time":330128,"text":"In other words, precisely those beings"},{"time":332313,"text":"who have created the technologies"},{"time":334646,"text":"that override so many\nof the limits of old,"},{"time":338196,"text":"are the ones wisest\nabout the need for limits,"},{"time":341207,"text":"even when it comes to technology."},{"time":344883,"text":"I once went to the Google headquarters"},{"time":347512,"text":"and I saw all the things\nmany of you have heard about;"},{"time":350315,"text":"the indoor tree houses, the trampolines,"},{"time":353539,"text":"workers at that time enjoying 20 percent\nof their paid time free"},{"time":358017,"text":"so that they could just let\ntheir imaginations go wandering."},{"time":362057,"text":"But what impressed me even more"},{"time":364975,"text":"was that as I was waiting\nfor my digital I.D.,"},{"time":368554,"text":"one Googler was telling me\nabout the program"},{"time":371323,"text":"that he was about to start\nto teach the many, many Googlers"},{"time":375117,"text":"who practice yoga\nto become trainers in it,"},{"time":378510,"text":"and the other Googler was telling me\nabout the book that he was about to write"},{"time":382764,"text":"on the inner search engine,"},{"time":385778,"text":"and the ways in which science\nhas empirically shown"},{"time":388771,"text":"that sitting still, or meditation,"},{"time":391308,"text":"can lead not just to better \nhealth or to clearer thinking,"},{"time":394920,"text":"but even to emotional intelligence."},{"time":398440,"text":"I have another friend in Silicon Valley"},{"time":400753,"text":"who is really one \nof the most eloquent spokesmen"},{"time":403875,"text":"for the latest technologies,"},{"time":405678,"text":"and in fact was one of the founders\nof Wired magazine, Kevin Kelly."},{"time":409563,"text":"And Kevin wrote his last book\non fresh technologies"},{"time":413316,"text":"without a smartphone\nor a laptop or a TV in his home."},{"time":417879,"text":"And like many in Silicon Valley,"},{"time":420761,"text":"he tries really hard to observe"},{"time":423737,"text":"what they call an Internet sabbath,"},{"time":427643,"text":"whereby for 24 or 48 hours every week"},{"time":430741,"text":"they go completely offline"},{"time":433821,"text":"in order to gather the sense of direction"},{"time":435969,"text":"and proportion they'll need \nwhen they go online again."},{"time":439463,"text":"The one thing perhaps\nthat technology hasn't always given us"},{"time":443190,"text":"is a sense of how to make\nthe wisest use of technology."},{"time":447899,"text":"And when you speak of the sabbath,"},{"time":450564,"text":"look at the Ten Commandments --"},{"time":452501,"text":"there's only one word there\nfor which the adjective \"holy\" is used,"},{"time":456874,"text":"and that's the Sabbath."},{"time":459150,"text":"I pick up the Jewish holy book\nof the Torah --"},{"time":462180,"text":"its longest chapter, it's on the Sabbath."},{"time":465521,"text":"And we all know that it's really\none of our greatest luxuries,"},{"time":469418,"text":"the empty space."},{"time":471606,"text":"In many a piece of music, \nit's the pause or the rest"},{"time":475528,"text":"that gives the piece\nits beauty and its shape."},{"time":478638,"text":"And I know I as a writer"},{"time":480221,"text":"will often try to include\na lot of empty space on the page"},{"time":484354,"text":"so that the reader can complete\nmy thoughts and sentences"},{"time":488066,"text":"and so that her imagination\nhas room to breathe."}]},{"cues":[{"time":493618,"text":"Now, in the physical domain, \nof course, many people,"},{"time":496196,"text":"if they have the resources,"},{"time":497720,"text":"will try to get a place in the country,\na second home."},{"time":501200,"text":"I've never begun to have those resources,"},{"time":504342,"text":"but I sometimes remember\nthat any time I want,"},{"time":508057,"text":"I can get a second home in time,\nif not in space,"},{"time":512422,"text":"just by taking a day off."},{"time":514853,"text":"And it's never easy because, of course, \nwhenever I do I spend much of it"},{"time":518418,"text":"worried about all the extra stuff"},{"time":520096,"text":"that's going to crash down on me\nthe following day."},{"time":522770,"text":"I sometimes think I'd rather give up\nmeat or sex or wine"},{"time":525792,"text":"than the chance to check on my emails."},{"time":527834,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":528958,"text":"And every season I do try to take\nthree days off on retreat"},{"time":533266,"text":"but a part of me still feels guilty\nto be leaving my poor wife behind"},{"time":537568,"text":"and to be ignoring\nall those seemingly urgent emails"},{"time":540616,"text":"from my bosses"},{"time":542370,"text":"and maybe to be missing\na friend's birthday party."},{"time":545437,"text":"But as soon as I get\nto a place of real quiet,"},{"time":549265,"text":"I realize that it's only by going there"},{"time":551734,"text":"that I'll have anything fresh\nor creative or joyful to share"},{"time":555761,"text":"with my wife or bosses or friends."},{"time":558267,"text":"Otherwise, really,"},{"time":559547,"text":"I'm just foisting on them\nmy exhaustion or my distractedness,"},{"time":563067,"text":"which is no blessing at all."}]},{"cues":[{"time":566849,"text":"And so when I was 29,"},{"time":569317,"text":"I decided to remake my entire life"},{"time":572382,"text":"in the light of going nowhere."},{"time":575099,"text":"One evening I was coming back\nfrom the office,"},{"time":577600,"text":"it was after midnight, I was in a taxi\ndriving through Times Square,"},{"time":581779,"text":"and I suddenly realized\nthat I was racing around so much"},{"time":585279,"text":"I could never catch up with my life."},{"time":588435,"text":"And my life then, as it happened,"},{"time":590251,"text":"was pretty much the one\nI might have dreamed of as a little boy."},{"time":594072,"text":"I had really interesting friends\nand colleagues,"},{"time":596387,"text":"I had a nice apartment\non Park Avenue and 20th Street."},{"time":600635,"text":"I had, to me, a fascinating job \nwriting about world affairs,"},{"time":605068,"text":"but I could never separate myself\nenough from them"},{"time":608056,"text":"to hear myself think --"},{"time":609759,"text":"or really, to understand\nif I was truly happy."},{"time":613885,"text":"And so, I abandoned my dream life"},{"time":617072,"text":"for a single room on the backstreets\nof Kyoto, Japan,"},{"time":622382,"text":"which was the place\nthat had long exerted a strong,"},{"time":625668,"text":"really mysterious gravitational pull on me."},{"time":629518,"text":"Even as a child"},{"time":630853,"text":"I would just look at a painting\nof Kyoto and feel I recognized it;"},{"time":634224,"text":"I knew it before I ever laid eyes on it."},{"time":637471,"text":"But it's also, as you all know,"},{"time":639400,"text":"a beautiful city encircled by hills,"},{"time":642119,"text":"filled with more than 2,000 temples\nand shrines,"},{"time":645748,"text":"where people have been sitting still\nfor 800 years or more."},{"time":650860,"text":"And quite soon after I moved there,\nI ended up where I still am"},{"time":654853,"text":"with my wife, formerly our kids,"},{"time":657432,"text":"in a two-room apartment\nin the middle of nowhere"},{"time":660013,"text":"where we have no bicycle, no car,"},{"time":662401,"text":"no TV I can understand,"},{"time":664570,"text":"and I still have to support my loved ones"},{"time":667123,"text":"as a travel writer and a journalist,"},{"time":669654,"text":"so clearly this is not ideal\nfor job advancement"},{"time":673018,"text":"or for cultural excitement"},{"time":674845,"text":"or for social diversion."},{"time":677212,"text":"But I realized that it gives me\nwhat I prize most,"},{"time":682400,"text":"which is days"},{"time":684040,"text":"and hours."},{"time":685773,"text":"I have never once had to use\na cell phone there."},{"time":688400,"text":"I almost never have to look at the time,"},{"time":691943,"text":"and every morning when I wake up,"},{"time":694497,"text":"really the day stretches in front of me"},{"time":696858,"text":"like an open meadow."},{"time":699832,"text":"And when life throws up\none of its nasty surprises,"},{"time":703028,"text":"as it will, more than once,"},{"time":704989,"text":"when a doctor comes into my room"},{"time":707170,"text":"wearing a grave expression,"},{"time":709065,"text":"or a car suddenly veers\nin front of mine on the freeway,"},{"time":712693,"text":"I know, in my bones,"},{"time":715437,"text":"that it's the time I've spent\ngoing nowhere"},{"time":718147,"text":"that is going to sustain me much more"},{"time":720149,"text":"than all the time I've spent\nracing around to Bhutan or Easter Island."}]},{"cues":[{"time":726306,"text":"I'll always be a traveler --"},{"time":727710,"text":"my livelihood depends on it --"},{"time":729614,"text":"but one of the beauties of travel"},{"time":731793,"text":"is that it allows you to bring stillness"},{"time":735899,"text":"into the motion and the commotion\nof the world."},{"time":740019,"text":"I once got on a plane\nin Frankfurt, Germany,"},{"time":743397,"text":"and a young German woman \ncame down and sat next to me"},{"time":746345,"text":"and engaged me\nin a very friendly conversation"},{"time":748965,"text":"for about 30 minutes,"},{"time":750716,"text":"and then she just turned around"},{"time":752709,"text":"and sat still for 12 hours."},{"time":755982,"text":"She didn't once turn on her video monitor,"},{"time":758616,"text":"she never pulled out a book,\nshe didn't even go to sleep,"},{"time":761911,"text":"she just sat still,"},{"time":764698,"text":"and something of her clarity and calm\nreally imparted itself to me."},{"time":769999,"text":"I've noticed more and more people\ntaking conscious measures these days"},{"time":774321,"text":"to try to open up a space\ninside their lives."},{"time":777605,"text":"Some people go to black-hole resorts"},{"time":779935,"text":"where they'll spend hundreds\nof dollars a night"},{"time":782295,"text":"in order to hand over\ntheir cell phone and their laptop"},{"time":785453,"text":"to the front desk on arrival."},{"time":787657,"text":"Some people I know,\njust before they go to sleep,"},{"time":790622,"text":"instead of scrolling through\ntheir messages"},{"time":792746,"text":"or checking out YouTube,"},{"time":794418,"text":"just turn out the lights\nand listen to some music,"},{"time":797662,"text":"and notice that they sleep much better"},{"time":800088,"text":"and wake up much refreshed."},{"time":803301,"text":"I was once fortunate enough"},{"time":805507,"text":"to drive into the high, dark mountains\nbehind Los Angeles,"},{"time":810547,"text":"where the great poet and singer"},{"time":813095,"text":"and international heartthrob Leonard Cohen"},{"time":816317,"text":"was living and working for many years\nas a full-time monk"},{"time":820488,"text":"in the Mount Baldy Zen Center."},{"time":823339,"text":"And I wasn't entirely surprised"},{"time":825304,"text":"when the record that he released\nat the age of 77,"},{"time":829014,"text":"to which he gave the deliberately \nunsexy title of \"Old Ideas,\""},{"time":834296,"text":"went to number one in the charts \nin 17 nations in the world,"},{"time":837258,"text":"hit the top five in nine others."},{"time":840488,"text":"Something in us, I think, is crying out"},{"time":843255,"text":"for the sense of intimacy and depth\nthat we get from people like that."},{"time":847761,"text":"who take the time\nand trouble to sit still."},{"time":851543,"text":"And I think many\nof us have the sensation,"},{"time":853781,"text":"I certainly do,"},{"time":855309,"text":"that we're standing about two inches away\nfrom a huge screen,"},{"time":859767,"text":"and it's noisy and it's crowded"},{"time":861605,"text":"and it's changing with every second,"},{"time":863781,"text":"and that screen is our lives."},{"time":866530,"text":"And it's only by stepping back,\nand then further back,"},{"time":870153,"text":"and holding still,"},{"time":871891,"text":"that we can begin to see\nwhat the canvas means"},{"time":874709,"text":"and to catch the larger picture."},{"time":877005,"text":"And a few people do that for us\nby going nowhere."}]},{"cues":[{"time":881950,"text":"So, in an age of acceleration,"},{"time":883972,"text":"nothing can be more exhilarating\nthan going slow."},{"time":888021,"text":"And in an age of distraction,"},{"time":890202,"text":"nothing is so luxurious\nas paying attention."},{"time":894715,"text":"And in an age of constant movement,"},{"time":897441,"text":"nothing is so urgent as sitting still."},{"time":901214,"text":"So you can go on your next vacation"},{"time":903443,"text":"to Paris or Hawaii, or New Orleans;"},{"time":906509,"text":"I bet you'll have a wonderful time."},{"time":910049,"text":"But, if you want to come back home\nalive and full of fresh hope,"},{"time":915117,"text":"in love with the world,"},{"time":917277,"text":"I think you might want\nto try considering going nowhere."},{"time":921713,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":922860,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}